imdb.plot outline: The Titanic Channel, a global OTT Channel, rounds up the word's most researched and respected group of Expert Hosts on the world famous topic of RMS Titanic. Our archive of 300+ episodes includes an elite group of storytellers enticing a diverse audience on a vast range of topics relating to the story of Titanic including: the tragic and heroic tales of the ship's passengers and crew, the intricacies and complexities of the ship's engineering and design, the science and ocean exploration of Titanic's final resting place, the market for its artifacts, Titanic's impact on today's pop culture, and a wide coverage of Titanic-related locations worldwide, including museums, memorials, monuments and events.
imdb.title: The Titanic Channel
plot: A Global OTT Channel Featuring Original Shows and Features on All Things Titanic.

_The Titanic Channel_ (qv), a global OTT Channel, rounds up the word's most researched and respected group of Expert Hosts on the world famous topic of RMS Titanic. Our archive of 300+ episodes includes an elite group of storytellers enticing a diverse audience on a vast range of topics relating to the story of Titanic including: the tragic and heroic tales of the ship's passengers and crew, the intricacies and complexities of the ship's engineering and design, the science and ocean exploration of Titanic's final resting place, the market for its artifacts, Titanic's impact on today's pop culture, and a wide coverage of Titanic-related locations worldwide, including museums, memorials, monuments and events.
